Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:82850,87330}THE CAPTURE OF THE ROBBER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138320,139540}Well, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139560,140750}{\i1}Goodbye!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140780,142570}The weather is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145150,148820}Even in such a cold morning, I have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148820,151660}Today you have many patients with fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152930,154540}You can play with the snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154630,156810}but be careful not to get fever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156840,157690}{\i1}Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160480,162260}The handle is frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162540,164920}I wonder if it crashes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166490,168180}Well, I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168180,169190}{\i1}Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171380,173680}{\i1}Even this is frozen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173870,177190}{\i1}How did my mother boil tea for breakfast?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177580,180840}{\i1}That's it, I will test the boiler!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182070,183160}Ah hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198410,200700}Lassie, what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200830,203880}You see, this is your first winter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204120,206350}Although you seem very big...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207170,208800}It's snow! The snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209010,211690}Today it's snowing, this weather is cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212610,214060}Look at this, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214270,216590}The road and the roof and\Neverything is white, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217520,218740}{\i1}As expected, from this morning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218770,220880}{\i1}even Grandma Forrest closed the window!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224830,228820}From there, she still watches\Noutside the house as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229010,230070}Well, Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230320,232040}I will leave the house under your care today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233000,234870}Don't show this sad face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235290,238810}I'm sure you'll be used to staying\Nat home until I come back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238910,240080}When I come back we'll play together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240160,241900}I will let you go in snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241980,242810}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330380,332640}Colin is absent because he has fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332840,336850}and Sandy can't ride the bike\Nbecause of the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358650,360290}John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360480,362190}Stop staring outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362450,363130}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363160,364120}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371260,373050}Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373760,376230}You know that you get a penalty when\Nyou're late without an excuse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376340,380920}Yes. We used the sleigh for our preparation,\Nwhich took a long time to get it ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380980,382100}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382210,384150}Take off your coat and take your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384200,385010}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394110,395790}Colin took a vacation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395810,396970}He has fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397060,401880}Listen, my grandfather made me cookies\Nand I put it in my coat, outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401910,402550}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402600,404180}Want to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409220,409920}{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410110,411390}{\i1}What about Lassie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411640,412390}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412420,414970}I usually leave it in the backyard to play there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415260,416580}Today it is inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416740,418470}Have you locked the doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418600,420070}I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421080,425460}If it feels bored, I hope not to cause\Nchaos inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537480,538570}Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554880,556260}I feel sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556290,557680}The weather is very cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557810,560010}However, I can't resist not the drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563780,565750}Hey, what is it, dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565750,568020}Why did you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568300,570600}Look, this is the same as machine oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570620,573670}Without this thing, my body\Nwill not hold up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573690,575720}I can't put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575740,578960}I'm hiding here until I drink as I please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580000,581720}You want to try it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581820,583290}You will feel warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583410,583860}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587520,588110}Pfff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588140,590900}That's why I hate dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590980,592750}Does the smell of wine is really strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631510,636120}Maybe everyone is having fun now\Nand making a snowman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636610,637230}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645000,646010}{\i1}Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648570,650950}Lassie! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651080,653410}You shouldn't be in such a cold place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655360,658640}I'm also on my own now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671710,674460}{\i1}Does everyone is having fun?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674780,677620}{\i1}My father delivers the goods through the snow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677790,681180}{\i1}My mother took my little brother\Nand went to Dr. Hooper.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681560,683540}My little brother has fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683780,685530}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686500,688910}But when you are beside me\NI feel more comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688980,692600}All I do is read books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693560,695270}Don't look here and there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695370,698280}The place is a mess and I feel embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702190,705370}Come here, Lassie! It's warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709160,712220}I have no friends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712670,715420}You are the first to enter my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715900,717990}John and the others haven't come yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719360,723820}I don't know anyone other than John,\NI can talk to him with all ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724380,725990}I'm very shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726590,729610}What should I do to come John and Sandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730340,730900}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730930,732050}Ah, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732550,734450}Do you look at the strange shape?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734590,736110}{\i1}I made it badly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736200,737920}{\i1}I'm a little bad at manual work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738320,742270}Our store uses these mobile machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742410,745330}I used to buy things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746670,747560}{\i1}Look!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747660,749720}{\i1}It is small, but it moves correctly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750270,754160}These is just a motor ship\Non the river, but it moves fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755040,758010}I wonder why I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758290,761540}I'm not quite sure of myself\Nto be a dynamic person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763220,765540}I don't have any!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766580,770100}I have no choice but to read novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770540,773090}Anything can be done in books.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774390,778090}The book I'm reading now\Nis "The Dog of Baskerville".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778440,781110}And it's about a dog\Nturned into a big monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781310,783940}This great mystery has been\Nfollowed by a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784850,788010}I love Sherlock Holmes because he is fast-paced!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788490,789740}He is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789880,793460}Lassie, what would you say\Nif you were in his place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794430,795620}Are you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795780,797780}Well, let's sleep together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798680,799540}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799570,800790}It's very warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802820,806030}In any case, you don't understand\Nwhat people are saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822470,824630}Lassie, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828720,831050}I understand, do you want to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832070,833400}Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836240,837700}The snowing has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838200,840420}It's okay to go out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840680,842010}But the weather is still cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845320,847160}Come back again, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849340,852570}In fact, I don't want you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852890,854850}Yet I will let it go on its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855700,858800}But Lassie was very warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880620,885840}This means that the war\Nlasted for 100 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886130,887400}Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887560,888420}Oh? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888570,892660}Who was the ruler of England\Nwhen the war started?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893220,896120}He was the Black Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896980,898060}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898390,901650}Which caused the suffering of the French.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901650,902620}Who is it, Spinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904490,905420}Spinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905420,906270}Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906380,908550}What did you say about Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910010,912650}Focus on the lesson while explaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914480,915300}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915410,916320}Spinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933580,935120}What is all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939730,941010}Horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941100,942780}It's my coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942800,944320}Mine also!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944470,947440}Who did such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947770,948940}{\i1}No, that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949080,950630}{\i1}The culprit is just an animal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951000,954880}Is it an animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955230,956540}Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958040,960470}This thing is not worth any fuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960680,962860}Go back to the classroom and\Nprepare for the next lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963380,964240}You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964440,966690}What's the problem if it's a bit dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966780,970440}But in my pocket it were cookies\Nand it had eaten all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970780,974220}Teacher, is not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974370,976440}{\i1}Teacher, there is a strange dog!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976760,978420}It's wearing a shawl around its neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978820,980150}{\i1}A dog?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980270,981230}{\i1}Where? Where?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981300,982780}{\i1}I really took the shawl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982880,984430}It's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985990,986900}Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988410,989400}It barked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989430,991190}- Maybe he is a predator!\N- Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991430,992900}John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993110,994690}Is this your dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994720,995700}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995890,998170}The school if for study only!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998320,1000250}You don't have to bring a dog here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000390,1001480}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001590,1004380}I will try to get it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004440,1005770}Okay, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006460,1008440}Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008570,1009830}{\i1}It may bite you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009890,1011800}Teacher! Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011930,1013040}It escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013060,1014030}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014110,1015470}Well, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015950,1018020}Please stop! Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018040,1020180}All of you, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020920,1024740}Wait...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024830,1027280}Children, come back immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027780,1028730}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029420,1031530}Strange, since when Lassie...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031560,1032820}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032840,1034370}Hurry up and stop everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034430,1035720}But, Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035750,1037570}Aren't you its owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037570,1041240}The shawl it was wearing wasn't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041340,1043360}Spinner ah, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043560,1044300}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044450,1047260}Just before I saw the dog wearing\Na green-colored shawl, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047380,1049240}My shawl is brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049320,1052800}Also how can Lassie wrap\Nthe shawl around its neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052930,1053760}Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053860,1057160}It's better to follow everyone,\Nbecause the dog is not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064870,1066370}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066390,1067790}Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068060,1070180}All of you, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079300,1081410}Well, we have besieged it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082500,1084230}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086130,1088300}Well, now I will deal with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088450,1090220}Wait, what if it's not guilty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090330,1091320}But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091410,1093140}Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093280,1094540}Lassie didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094660,1096920}Spinner's shawl is different from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097060,1098770}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098960,1101450}There is no one else to steal the other shawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101540,1104840}Also, you're trying to say that\Nyou know who the culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105190,1107830}I don't know who did it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108160,1109290}You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109290,1110340}You are wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110340,1113650}Spinner, please explain to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114060,1114920}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115100,1115740}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115850,1118280}Spinner is not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120530,1123810}Spinner! Make an effort, faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125820,1127860}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128770,1129900}These tracks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129990,1131770}...go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132030,1133180}It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135000,1137000}If these were made by the culprit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137160,1138680}and it wasn't your dog
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138830,1141650}we will know the perpetrator\Nonly if we see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141910,1143750}Carraclough, step aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144130,1146070}Let me look inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154920,1156170}It's angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157010,1158390}Look, as I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158540,1160530}Caraclough, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165770,1167830}Lassie, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181300,1182940}Let's take a look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183400,1184930}We won't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189840,1190910}Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203580,1206530}Carraclough, is anything in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207970,1209360}Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211400,1213140}Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219910,1221620}- Oh really?\N- Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222210,1223350}Those two blows?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223480,1225110}{\i1}Also her puppies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226290,1228990}It's my shawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229410,1230880}But it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230970,1232380}That these blows should be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232660,1236250}The beatings are still so satisfying\Nthat I stayed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236440,1239340}Yes, isn't it better to leave it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239480,1240930}It's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241230,1243400}This is the school's warehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247290,1248580}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248680,1252560}But I will leave her until\Nher puppies stop breastfeeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252750,1254270}That's great, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255680,1257360}I'm sorry, John, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257460,1258490}Sorry, John...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258570,1260060}You're a clever dog, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260080,1261740}A beautiful shawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261880,1263430}Go back after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263490,1265870}{\i1}So, the teacher said!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266910,1268450}{\i1}Colin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268570,1270540}{\i1}Hey Colin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271210,1272240}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272700,1273730}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274030,1276580}Lassie, was the shawl warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277110,1280330}This shawl is especially from Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280710,1284480}Today, there was a thief in school,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284670,1287710}but Lassie managed to find the real culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288680,1289470}Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289820,1291120}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291170,1293490}{\i1}Yes, it's like a detective!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293490,1297610}Lassie, did you remember\Nwhat I was telling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301180,1302100}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302250,1303780}You remembered then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304030,1305510}Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307340,1310760}Hey Colin, will you come to school tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310810,1311470}{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318860,1321080}{\i1}I had quarreled with Sandy at school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.39,0:22:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321390,1323630}{\i1}Lassie, you are the reason!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323750,1326260}{\i1}This is because you are\Nfollowing me like a fool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326380,1327250}{\i1}You act with dignity,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327400,1329370}{\i1}but you can't do anything without me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329550,1331130}{\i1}Don't follow me anymore!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331440,1333840}{\i1}Next episode:\NI DON'T LIKE LASSIE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.98,0:22:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333980,1335300}{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
